# =================================================================
# 3. Whitelist (What TO show on GitHub)
# =================================================================
# Explicitly keep these top-level files
!README.md
!structure.md
!.gitignore

# Explicitly keep the entire Source_code directory
!Source_code/**

# Explicitly keep the Download directory and its versioned files
!Download/**
# Ensure we don't accidentally hide versioned binaries in Download/Windows
!Download/Windows/*.exe
!Download/Windows/*.zip